f-time\">14:18<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"notif-seen\">✓ seen<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"notif-card seen\">\n            <div class=\"notif-header\"><div class=\"nd green\"><\u002Fdiv><div class=\"notif-type green\">✓ Colour change<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n            <div class=\"notif-text\">No.4 Baradar — purple &amp; pink. Updated in stewards view automatically.<\u002Fdiv>\n            <div class=\"notif-footer\"><div class=\"notif-time\">14:11<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"notif-seen\">✓ seen<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"notif-section-label\">Earlier today · Race 2<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"notif-card earlier\">\n            <div class=\"notif-header\"><div class=\"nd green\"><\u002Fdiv><div class=\"notif-type green\">✓ SS confirmed<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n            <div class=\"notif-text\">R2 — no issues. Stewards satisfied.<\u002Fdiv>\n            <div class=\"notif-footer\"><div class=\"notif-time\">13:52<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"notif-seen\">✓ seen<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"notif-card earlier\">\n            <div class=\"notif-header\"><div class=\"nd grey\"><\u002Fdiv><div class=\"notif-type grey\">Going update<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n            <div class=\"notif-text\">Going updated Good to Firm. LPS updated. Judges notified.<\u002Fdiv>\n            <div class=\"notif-footer\"><div class=\"notif-time\">13:48<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"notif-seen\">✓ seen<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"notif-section-label\">Earlier today · Race 1<\u002Fdiv>\n          <div class=\"notif-card earlier\">\n            <div class=\"notif-header\"><div class=\"nd green\"><\u002Fdiv><div class=\"notif-type green\">✓ SS confirmed<\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n            <div class=\"notif-text\">R1 — weighed in 13:12.<\u002Fdiv>\n            <div class=\"notif-footer\"><div class=\"notif-time\">13:12<\u002Fdiv><div class=\"notif-see